  <brief_title>Evaluation of the Deep TMS H-Coil in the Treatment of Major Depression- Augmentation of Antidepressant Medication</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the H-Coil Transcranial Magnetic Stimulation(TMS) Device- Augmentation for Drug Resistant Depression</official_title>
