  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of the novel deep TMS H-Coil design as an augmentation measure in the treatment of
      medication resistant major depression. Stimulation is administered with and without
      cognitive-emotional provocation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
