  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients diagnosed as suffering from treatment resistant major depression

          -  Right laterality

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  other major axis I diagnosis

          -  severe axis II diagnosis

          -  risk factors to convulsions

          -  history of drug abuse in the past year
      </textblock>
